<L>__{4. interior club entrance}
<A>__{as short round hurries toward the exit, he bumps into a man in a tuxedo entering the club. short round looks up at the man, but we don't see his face. then short round is grabbed by the scruff of his neck and a door man hustles him out the door, short round yelling insults all the way. a maitre d' apologizes to the man in the tuxedo and two hat check girls smile at him familiarly as he continues into the ballroom. we notice something incongruous: the man in the tuxedo is wear ing work boots caked with mud.}
